<subSubSection pageId="633" pageNumber="634" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="633" pageNumber="634">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="633" pageNumber="634">This species is found from southwestern New Brunswick (Webster and Bousquet 2008: 20) to eastern South Dakota (Kirk and Balsbaugh 1975: 35; French et al. 2004: 557), south to east-central Texas (Brazos County, CNC; Riley 2011), northern Georgia (Ball 1959: 216-217), and northwestern South Carolina (Ciegler 2000: 85).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
